equipower resources corp
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Utilities
Industry: Utilities
Sub-Industry: Power Generation
EquiPower Resources Corp. generates, transmits, and distributes electricity. The Company operates cycle natural gas fired power plants to produces electricity. EquiPower Resources serves customers in the United States.




